[
  {
    "id": "thermal-tab",
    "type": "tab",
    "label": "Thermal Tanks",
    "disabled": false,
    "info": "Thermal tank Supervisor dashboard v0.4.2\n\nPOST endpoint:   /thermal/ingest  (pushed by the thermal-analyzer container)\nThermal API:     flow.thermal_base (default resolved from hostname, override with THERMAL_API)\n\nGroups (page width = 24 cells):\n  • Overview       — full-width site header + deep link to operator console\n  • Tank Config    — collapsed panel: rename tanks, override medium (water/oil/auto)\n  • Live View      — MJPEG stream (width 14)\n  • Tanks          — per-tank KPI cards stacked vertically (width 10, sidebar)\n  • Trends         — 24 h level & temperature history\n  • Alerts         — persisted out-of-band history (bounded 200 rows)\n  • Events         — raw ingest log (collapsed)\n\nUser-configurable overrides live in flow.context('tank_overrides') = {\n  '<tank_id>': { name: '<display name>', medium: 'auto' | 'water' | 'oil' }\n}\nOverrides are applied inside ingest-process before any downstream rendering.\n"
  },
